data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of a pristine waterfront community, where luxury meets serenity. This newly constructed 2-bedroom 2-bath condo is the epitome of modern living, offering a perfect blend of sophistication and comfort. Every detail has been meticulously crafted for your comfort and style. The kitchen boasts state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances, complemented by sleek granite countertops. Experience the warmth of home with a thoughtfully designed layout featuring LPV and carpet flooring throughout. The open concept seamlessly connects the living and dining areas, creating a welcoming space for relaxation and entertainment. Escape to your private balcony and savor breathtaking views of the waterfront. Whether you're enjoying a morning coffee or unwinding after a long day, the balcony provides the perfect vantage point to soak in the beauty of your surroundings. Under construction, pictures are coming soon.
